column16: Denard Span homers (2) on a fly ball to right field.    Danny Espinosa scores.    Dan Uggla scores.
Clint Robinson flies out to left fielder Kelly Johnson in foul territory.
Dan Uggla singles on a line drive to left fielder Kelly Johnson.   Wilson Ramos scores.    Danny Espinosa to 2nd.
Danny Espinosa singles on a ground ball to right fielder Nick Markakis.   Wilson Ramos to 2nd.
Ryan Zimmerman flies out to center fielder Eric Young Jr.
